com.microsoft.azure.webjobs.script.binding

Class BindingDataStore

  • java.lang.Object
    • com.microsoft.azure.webjobs.script.binding.BindingDataStore

  • public final class BindingDataStore
extends java.lang.Object
    A warehouse storing all binding related information including actual binding value as well as binding declaration info. This warehouse also provides methods to validate/look-up/convert against Java types. Thread-safety: Single thread.
